":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"Jeffares, Neil","attributedYear":2016,"wikidata":"Q60311889"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 4241, Recto","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"vol.20, p.191","type":"R\u00e9f\u00e9rence de l\u0027inventaire manuscrit"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Arts graphiques","printsDrawingsEntity":"Cabinet des dessins","printsDrawingsCollection":"Fonds des dessins et miniatures","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0.044","displayDimension":"0.044 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0.034","displayDimension":"0.034 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Pastel sur papier bleu coll\u00e9 sur un carton. Les mesures du cadre sont : H : 00,625 ; L : 00,52 et profondeur : 00,125.\nLa restauration de cette \u0153uvre a \u00e9t\u00e9 rendue possible gr\u00e2ce au soutien de M. et Mme Patrick A. Gerschel avec la collaboration des American Friends of the Louvre en 2014.","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection de Joseph Ricard, p\u00e8re de l\u0027enfant, secr\u00e9taire de l\u0027Intendance de Bourgogne. Puis au mod\u00e8le et \u00e0 son \u00e9poux Alexandre Claude Goujon. Probablement \u00e0 leur fils Jean-Marie Claude Alexandre Goujon (1768-1795), d\u00e9put\u00e9 de Seine-et-Oise \u00e0 la Convention, et \u00e0 son \u00e9pouse Lise Cormery (1771-1843), puis peut-\u00eatre \u00e0 leur fils unique Philar\u00e8te (1794-1832), architecte. Acquis en 1898 de la famille Goujon par Marie-Louise Jeanne Peyrat, marquise Arconati-Visconti (1840-1923). Collection Arconati-Visconti. Don par la marquise Arconati-Visconti au mus\u00e9e du Louvre le 17 mars 1914, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 11 novembre 1916. Restaur\u00e9 en 2015, gr\u00e2ce au soutien de M. et Mme Patrick A. Gerschel, avec la collaboration des American Friends of the Louvre (d\u00e9cadrage, d\u00e9poussi\u00e9rage de l\u0027arri\u00e8re du carton, \u00e9limination m\u00e9canique des moisissures \u00e0 l\u0027aide d\u0027un pinceau et des d\u00e9jections d\u0027insectes, gommage du verso du carton et refixage ponctuel des soul\u00e8vements de papier par du papier japonais teint\u00e9 en bleu et de la m\u00e9thylcellulose \u00e0 l\u0027angle sup\u00e9rieur gauche et au bord gauche, r\u00e9encadrement dans un cadre embo\u00eetant).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Derni\u00e8re provenance : Arconati Visconti, Marie","note":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"startYear":1914,"endYear":null}]}],"ownedBy":"","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"collection":[{"value":"Arconati Visconti"}],"person":[{"value":"Goujon, Mme, n\u00e9e Nicole Ricard"},{"value":"Ricard, Nicole"}],"subject":[{"value":"portrait"}],"technic":[{"value":"pastel"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/01\/78\/47\/00\/AGO017847-000_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/01\/78\/47\/00\/AGO017847-000_PE.jpg","copyright":"GrandPalaisRmn (Mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Michel Urtado","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/01\/78\/47\/00\/AGO017847-001_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/01\/78\/47\/00\/AGO017847-001_PE.jpg","copyright":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, dist. GrandPalaisRmn \/ Martine Beck-Coppola","type":"Environnement","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/01\/78\/47\/00\/AGO017847-002_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/colle